        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Notum sit omnibus sanctae aecclesiae catholicae filiis, <persName
                            key="#Princeps #parentOf #grandparentOf #familyOf" ref="#people/3001"
                            >Richardum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principem</rs>
                        <rs key="#grandparentOf">avum</rs> meum <rs key="#Churches">aecclesias</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasteria</rs> dilexisse, <rs
                            key="#Private_foundations"><rs key="#Monasteries">cenovia</rs>
                            contruxisse</rs> inte que etiam et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Private_foundations"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3046">Sancti Angeli quod dicitur in
                            Formis</orgName> fecisse, eumque <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                                ><rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine"
                                >vineis</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Forests #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >silvis</rs></rs>, <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                                ><rs key="#Churches">ecclesiis</rs> ac diversis opibus</rs> ditasse.
                        Quo defuncto, <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf #familyOf"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordanum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principem</rs>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patrem</rs> meum omnia quae eidem monasterio Richardus
                        princeps <rs key="#parentOf">pater</rs> eius, avus meus dederat confirmasse,
                        ipsumque postmodum quam plurima eidem cenovio contulisse. Ego autem
                            <persName key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/3010"
                            >secundus Richardus</persName> divina ordinante clementia Capuanorum <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, pro salute animarum illorum principum <rs
                            key="#familyOf">parentum</rs> meorum et meae, ac ob statu nostri
                        principatus, <rs key="#Intercessory">interventu</rs> domni <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Prevosts #Personal_rank" ref="#people/4240"
                            >Petri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">prepositi</rs> eiusdem monasterii et domni <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Bishops #Personal_rank" ref="#people/3056"
                            >Iohannis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000">Aversani</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>, et <persName key="#Intercessory #Monks"
                            ref="#people/4241">Mainardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs>, et <persName key="#Intercessory"
                            ref="#people/4242">Rodulfi de Muce grossa</persName>, et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3078"
                            >Stantionis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vice principis</rs> ac <persName
                            key="#Writer #Intercessory #Judge" ref="#people/3012"
                            >Quiriaci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs>, omnia quae suprascripti principes iam
                        prephato monasterio Sancti Angeli subdito <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti Benedicti
                            Montis Casini</orgName>, cui domnus <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/2416">Oderisius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preest, dederunt, et per principalem scriptum
                        confirmaverunt, per huius concessionis meae paginam concedo et confirmo
                        etiam que ego ipse postea tribui, et quae eidem pertinent monasterio, et
                        quae possidet et dominatur. Illius vero loci <rs key="#Fines">finis</rs> in
                        quo positum est monasterium prescriptum, primum indico, sic concedens et
                        confirmo: ex una vero parte sunt <rs key="#Quarries">cave cimentareae</rs>,
                        qualiter pergitur per <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiam</rs><orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3818"> Sancti Marcelli</orgName>
                        et ad terram que dicitur de <placeName ref="#places/4551"
                            >Bertarischi</placeName>, et qualiter vadit per ipsa terra de
                        Bertarischi et vadit ad canalem quae descendit de Asculcule, et qualiter
                        ascendit per super adscriptum canalem directe ad trivium qui coniungitur
                        tres viae, una quae descendit ad Sanctum Marcum, et alia quae descendit ad
                        Sanctum Angelum, et alia ascendit ad Roccam, et inde qualiter ascendit per
                        super ascripta via quae aliquantulum vadit super cripta arenaria et vadit in
                        monticellum et ad planam superscripti monticelli, quae est super vallis quae
                        vocatur Venula, et incipiente per suprascripta plana per traversum per
                        canalem quae vocatur da Ficu fuscule directe in costa quae dicitur Turris
                        Vespulum usque in semitam quae descendit desuper ad suprascripta Rocca, et
                        descendit per ipsa semita in monticellum quae Rickibellum vocatur. Et inde
                        qualiter descendit ad terram <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3033">Sancti
                            Vincentii</orgName> et per terram <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2321"
                            >Sancti Benedicti Maioris</orgName> constructi in Capua, et aliquantulum
                        per terram Ausentii Imperatoris, et per terram Sancti Vincentii usque ad
                        superscriptas cavas cimentarias. Item concedo et confirmo predicto
                        monasterio quicquid continetur in cartula oblationis quam prescriptus
                        Richardus princeps avus meus eidem monasterio obtulit, videlicet: <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            ref="#places/4528">Sarzanum</placeName>, et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >homines</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terras</rs> a <placeName ref="#places/4529"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Coloni/tenants">Sancto Martino qui dicitur ad
                            Lavem</placeName>, et per ipsum <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Chestnuts #Coloni/tenants" ref="#places/4530"
                            >Battitizzum</placeName> ubi nunc sedent homines praescripti monasterii,
                        et usque ad <placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Coloni/tenants"
                            ref="#places/4531">Ventum vanum</placeName>. Concedo quoque et confirmo
                        prephato monasterio aecclesiae Sancti Angeli, <rs key="#Churches"
                            >aecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3061">Sanctae Agathe</orgName> sita foras <rs
                            key="#Walls">muro</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Walls" ref="#places/4000">Aversano</placeName> cum
                            <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et universis suis pertinentiis. In
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capua</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3063">Sancti Angeli de Olaldischi</orgName> cum
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >servis</rs> et universis suis pertinentiis. Et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3031">Sancti Benedicti Piczoli</orgName> cum <rs
                            key="#Churches">aecclesiis</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs> et universis suis pertinentiis. Et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches #Slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3060">Sancti Ruphi</orgName> cum omnibus <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Slave_labour #Slave"
                            >servis</rs> et universis suis pertinentiis foris et intus Capuae,
                        qualiter antiquitus pertinuerunt prephatae aecclesiae quovis modo, et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Forests #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">silvas</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Hay/fodder #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >pascua</rs> et <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludes</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquas</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fisheries #Fish">piscationes</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #Slave_labour #Slave">servos et ancillas et
                            curtisanos</rs> et <rs key="#Aldius">aldios et aldias</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Fines">finibus</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/4028"><geogName
                                key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Hay/fodder #Fish #Coloni/tenants #Fines #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Aldius #Slave"
                                ref="#estates/3030">Cantiae</geogName></placeName>, et universa quae
                        suprascripta aecclesia Sancti Ruphi et <rs key="#rectorOf">rectores</rs>
                        eius iam per triginta annos et eo amplius a parte principis Richardi avi
                        mei, et Iordanis principis patris mei tenuerunt et possiderunt. Quae etiam
                        aliquando fuerunt quorundam <rs key="#siblingOf">fratrum</rs>
                        <persName key="#childOf #siblingOf" ref="#people/4243">Guidonis</persName>
                        et <persName key="#childOf #siblingOf" ref="#people/4244"
                            >Landenulfi</persName> qui fuerunt <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>
                        cuiusdam <persName><name ref="Lando Caputus">Landonis qui dicebantur
                                Caputi</name></persName>, qui etiam predicti tempore predicti
                        Richardi principis avi mei contra eiusdem animam principis cogitaverunt, et
                        inimicos intra provinciam eius invitaverunt, celaverunt et annonam dederunt,
                        ob quas culpas <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >res illorum</rs> fisco prephati principis avi mei <rs
                            key="#Law #Lombard">secundum Langobardicam legem</rs> devenerunt. <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >Quae etiam et prephato Richardo principi avio meo et Iordano principi
                            patri meo, et michi per conventionem a Capuanis dimissa sunt</rs>, et
                        per sacramentum firmata, et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">homines</rs> de
                            <placeName key="#Villages/settlements #Coloni/tenants"
                            ref="#places/4544">Camiliano</placeName>, videlicet <rs key="#childOf"
                            >filios</rs> cuiusdam Summi; <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            >quae aecclesiae</rs> sunt intra Capuam. Concedo quoque et confirmo
                        prephato monasterio Sancti Angeli <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3058">Sancti Petri de Scaphati</orgName> cum <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasteriis</rs>, <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >servis</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et universis
                        suis pertinentiis, et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">homines</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> quae sunt in loco qui dicitur
                            ad<placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Landed_possessions #Coloni/tenants"
                            ref="#places/4533"> Sanctum Herasmum</placeName>, sicut continetur in
                            <rs key="#Cartula">cartula oblationis</rs> quam avus princeps Richardus
                        fecit exinde predicto monasterio, et pater meus Iordanus princeps
                        confirmavit, et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                                ><rs key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs> et <rs key="#Chestnuts"
                                >castanetum</rs></rs> quae sunt prope loco qui dicitur Battitizzu
                        pro servitio hospitum. Omnia autem prescripta prephato monasterio Sancti
                        Angeli in perpetuum confirmo et concedo ad possessionem te potestatem et
                        dominationem ipsius, et predicti domni Petri venerabilis prepositi eiusdem
                        et eius successoribus, faciendo exinde regulariter quicquid eis placuerit,
                        remota omni contrarietate et molestatione omnium mortalium. Quod si quis
                        huius mea concessionis et confirmationis pagine contemptor aut violator esse
                        presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">centum libras auri purissimi</rs>
                        persolvat: medietatem meo sacro palatio et medietatem prephato monasterio
                        Sancti Angeli et domno Petro venerabili preposito predicti monasterii
                        eiusque successoribus. Solutaque pena librarum haec mea concessio et
                        confirmatio firma munita atque inviolabilis maneat in perpetuum. Et ut hoc
                        firmius credatur et diligentius observetur, manu propria subscripsi et
                        nostri sigilli impressione iussi decorari et insigniri. (M) Ex iussione
                        serenissime potestatis, scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Intercessory #Judge" ref="#people/3012"
                            >Quiriacus</persName> iudex. In anno dominice incarnationis millesimo
                        nonogesimo quinto, et quinto decimo anno principatus ipsius domni <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/3010"
                            >Richardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosi</rs> principis. Datum
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000">Averse</placeName>, septimo
                        decimo kalendas octobris per indictionem quartam. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
